  "description": "<p>7月12日上午，微博上有消息称，前御泥坊董事长因劳累过度，急性脑血栓重度昏迷，其年仅36岁<strong>。事实上，这并非孤例。近年来因为过劳导致的突然死亡事件正不断给中国的企业家群体敲响警钟。本文回顾了最近几年因为过度劳累而过世的企业家，以追悼和缅怀他们在中国商界写下的一笔。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2ec5d427/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245038.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%A1%E6%B3%A5%E5%9D%8A%E8%91%A3%E4%BA%8B%E9%95%BF%E5%8E%BB%E4%B8%96+%E7%9B%98%E7%82%B9%E9%82%A3%E4%BA%9B%E8%BF%87%E5%8A%B3%E6%AD%BB%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E5%AE%B6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245038.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%A1%E6%B3%A5%E5%9D%8A%E8%91%A3%E4%BA%8B%E9%95%BF%E5%8E%BB%E4%B8%96+%E7%9B%98%E7%82%B9%E9%82%A3%E4%BA%9B%E8%BF%87%E5%8A%B3%E6%AD%BB%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E5%AE%B6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245038.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%A1%E6%B3%A5%E5%9D%8A%E8%91%A3%E4%BA%8B%E9%95%BF%E5%8E%BB%E4%B8%96+%E7%9B%98%E7%82%B9%E9%82%A3%E4%BA%9B%E8%BF%87%E5%8A%B3%E6%AD%BB%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E5%AE%B6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245038.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%A1%E6%B3%A5%E5%9D%8A%E8%91%A3%E4%BA%8B%E9%95%BF%E5%8E%BB%E4%B8%96+%E7%9B%98%E7%82%B9%E9%82%A3%E4%BA%9B%E8%BF%87%E5%8A%B3%E6%AD%BB%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E5%AE%B6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245038.